item.title: Meetup - Tuesday 31st January 2017 at The ODI Node in Leeds
item.description: Happy new year! it's time for the first devops get together of 2017 at the ODI Node in Leeds on Tuesday 31st January. We have a fantastic array of talks for you: 6:45 - 7:15 : Doors open, have a chat, make some new devops friends 7:15 - 7:30 : Group updates/news/announcements 7:30 - 8:05 :Lessons Learned From Continuous Delivery - Mandi Walls of Chef 8:05 - 8:20 : Intermission
